-26-13.png\" alt=\"2018-6-30-18-26-13\"></p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"成果\" style=\"position:relative;\">成果</h2>\n<p>如此一来，你开发的时候新开一个命令行窗口运行 <code class=\"language-text\">npm run dev-test</code> 就可以实时查看测试结果。\n如果你只想看一次结果，就只用运行 <code class=\"language-text\">npm run test</code></p>","frontmatter":{"title":"使用Karma+Mocha进行单元测试","date":"2018/08/25","description":null,"tags":["前端","测试"]}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/使用Karma-Mocha进行单元测试/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/移动端适配/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"移动端适配"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/常用正则表/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"常用正则表"}}}}}